entries.femaleVariant: Stop!
I'm here by contract, from a fixer, nothin' personal.
Fixer sent me.
GPS transmitter. The one you forgot to disable on the stolen meds.
GPS signal.
Sure, sure. And you be careful with that trigger.
Hand over the stolen meds and I'm gone.
Stolen?! Hahaha! The baloperidol doesn't work! S-so who's stealing from who?! Who?!
Stolen?! Hahaha! The baloperidol doesn't work! S-so who's stealing from who?! Who?!
Just hand 'em over and I'm gone.
H-how'd you find me?
Aaaargh! I’m not fucking crazy!
Baloperidol? For cyberpsychosis?
Easy, easy…
Sh-shut up! Go away!
If it doesn't work, give it to me.
Give it, or I call MaxTac.
This is our situation.
If they're no use to you, they don't work, just hand 'em over.
Ripperdocs! They're the real criminals!
You're the same as them… rippers, politicians… the same as that fucking Holt!
His death would change nothing.
You're a soldier, not a terrorist.
I see we're past talking.
Do what you want, but give me the drugs.
Listen, I don't really care.
Wanna murder a mayor? Fine. You think it'll make a difference? Sure, why not.
I just need those meds.
Ha, ha, ha… I see… It's all so clear…
Last marble just hit the floor. Can't let this drag on.
You're part of the system… a--a pawn in it… a slave to it…
Let's just fight.
We know where this's headed, rather not waste my time.
I appreciate your candor.
A Militech HKS-47 with polymer reinforcement. You were a soldier.
Militech. 3rd Light Division, 155th Infantry Regiment, 7 years in a fuckin' jungle… When times were simpler.
Before you got sick?
They cast me out like a dead battery.
I understand your anger.
Where did you serve?
You're angry, and I get it. You feel cheated.
Not just me!
I know, but if you zero Holt, you'll make it worse for everyone in your condition. They'll hunt you down.
Where'd you serve?
Brazil. R-remember all of it… Dirt on my face… F-fatigues always--always wet…
It's like a braindance I-I-I can't shut off…
The memories flood back?
Without the adrenaline. Without my brothers… Fuck! So quickly they forgot me…
It's campaign season. The first ribbon-cutter to push an anti-psycho policy after Holt's death is winnin' that election.
No! No, that's not true! The people will understand! The system will start to fall!
Everyone like you, they'll hunt you all down.
Leave… Go, please…
You know I can't without those meds.
Over there… I wanna be alone.
But… but soon… I'll find him. End him.
Other poltician's will make use of his death.
They'll say you're a psycho.
The death of one politician won't change anything.
If you kill Holt, first thing they'll do is brand you a psycho and a terrorist.
Uh-huh.
It will! These--these silver-tongue devils won't dare turn on their people ever again!
A line, I'm drawing a line! They can't treat us this way anymore! They--they--they can't use us anymore!
It’s not about ME! This is for everyone! All the sick!
No, this'd be a disservice to them. What're people gonna remember?
Cyberpsycho terrorist on one side, media-backed politicians on the other. Now, who's the crowd favorite?
I could think of a few differences.
Shut UP! That bastard, he stole from--from research! He doesn't care about the sick!
"Cyberpsycho assassin kills in cold blood." Who'd wanna help a monster like that?
Either you give me what you stole.
How--how can you work for them?
Or MaxTac swoops in, pays you a visit.
You ordinary… sell-out… piece of SHIT!!!
That's no reason to become a terrorist.
You hear that howling at night?
Like a dyin' animal. Waaargh! Aaaagh!
I know… And we can't ask them or we will repay them for the rest of our lives!
Shh, shh, quiet!
Ugh… Can't call the police  on him or it'll rile up the Tygers.
Gotta do somethin'! Can't have him here.
I don't know…
I told you not to move!
